## Burndown Tracking Workflow

- [ ] 1. Set baseline: Establish ideal burndown line from sprint commitment
- [ ] 2. Daily update: Track story points completed and remaining each day
- [ ] 3. Plot actual: Update the burndown chart with actual progress
- [ ] 4. Compare to ideal: Identify deviation from the ideal line
- [ ] 5. Diagnose issues: Why is actual ahead or behind ideal?
- [ ] 6. Course correct: Adjust scope, add resources, or revise timeline
- [ ] 7. Forecast: Predict whether sprint goal will be met

## Key Inputs
- Sprint goal: {{sprint_goal}}
- Total story points: {{total_story_points}}
- Sprint length: {{sprint_length}}
- Daily updates: {{daily_updates}}
